      "b": "15/17",
      "c": "16/17",
      "d": "13/17",
      "e": null
    },
    "section": "",
    "image": "",
    "answer": "b",
    "solution": "cotθ = 1/cosθ\n\n= 8/15(given)\n\ntanθ = 15/18\n\nBy Pythagoras theorem,\n\nx<sup>2</sup> = 152 + 82\n\nx2 = 225 + 64 = 289\n\nx = √289\n\n= 17\n\nHence sinθ = 15/x\n\n= 15/17",
    "examtype": "utme",
    "examyear": "2010"
