    "section": "",
    "image": "",
    "answer": "c",
    "solution": "x α 1/y .........(1)\n\nx = k x 1/y .........(2)\n\nWhen x = 2(1/2)\n\n= 5/2, y = 2\n\n(2) becomes 5/2 = k x 1/2\n\ngiving k = 5\n\nfrom (2), x = 5/y\n\nso when y =4, x = 5/y = 1(1/4)",
    "examtype": "utme",
